  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category</strong>: Clan<br /><strong>Prerequisite</strong>: Fujou Clan<br /><strong>Description</strong>: You become able to interweave curses into your normal speech, forcing creatures you talk with to reveal their secrets and be more wary of you. You gain the following:</p><ul><li>increase your wisdom ability score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li><li>You gain proficiency in the intimidation skill, if you already have proficiency, you gain expertise.</li><li>You can make wisdom (intimidation) checks, instead of charisma (intimidation) checks.</li><li>Once per casting, when a creature would fail a saving throw against a fujou hijutsu you cast, you can make one question of no more than 10 words, which the creature is compelled to answer truthfully.</li></ul>",
